parse.title: List of public libraries in Ontario

text.*:
This is a list of public libraries in Ontario.

Background[edit]

Ontario public libraries are created by municipal by-laws and governed by public library boards. The Ontario Ministry of Tourism and Culture[1] has responsibility for the administration of the Public Libraries Act.[2] The ministry's Culture Services Unit[3] provides support for the public library system and the Ontario Library Service deliver programs on behalf of the ministry.
